===Alternative forms===
In [[Traditional Chinese]], the component on the left of <code>U+79AE</code> is {{l|mul|礻}}. In Korean [[hanja]] and Japanese [[kyūjitai]], the component on the left of <code>U+79AE</code> is {{l|mul|示}} rather than {{l|mul|礻}}, which is also the historical form that appears in the [[w:Kangxi dictionary|Kangxi dictionary]]. A [[w:CJK compatibility ideographs|CJK compatibility ideograph]] exists at <code>U+F9B6</code> to reflect the form found in the Kangxi dictionary.

